### Login Alice (admin) — récupérer le token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "alice@example.com", "password": "password123" }

###

### Login Bob (member) — récupérer le token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "bob@example.com", "password": "password123" }

###

### Créer une tâche
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implémenter l'authentification JWT",
  "description": "Ajouter LocalStrategy et JwtStrategy via Passport",
  "status": "todo",
  "priority": "high",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}"
}

###

### Créer une tâche avec assignee
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Revoir la PR de Bob",
  "priority": "medium",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "assigneeId": "{{bobId}}"
}

###

### Lister toutes les tâches
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Récupérer une tâche par ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Tâche introuvable → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Modifier le statut d'une tâche
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "in_progress" }

###

### Assigner Bob à la tâche → déclenche task:assigned via WebSocket
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "assigneeId": "{{bobId}}" }

###

### Modifier priorité + titre
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implémenter JWT (révisé)",
  "priority": "low"
}

###

### Supprimer une tâche → 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
